<!-- 08 WHY US -->
<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">08 · Why homeowners call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Pro-style range expertise.</strong> Wolf DF, Viking 7, Thermador Pro Grand, BlueStar, Capital. Most LA appliance shops decline pro-style ranges or upcharge. We don't.</li>
